#   NOTE : Enter "Out Table Alias"
#   ex)
#       inputDataframe = inputs[0]
#       result = inputDataframe
#
import pandas as pd

data = inputs[0]

Q1 = data['weight'].quantile(0.25)
Q3 = data['weight'].quantile(0.75)
IQR = Q3-Q1

data['outlier'] = data['weight'].apply(lambda x : 1 if x<Q1-1.5*IQR else( 1 if x>Q3+1.5*IQR else 0))
